{"tid":450640,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 雲加宣佈退休，占士邦接任阿仙奴領隊","createTime":"2017-10-28T11:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T08:05:19.000Z","uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a5256eacfe8fc5127dcf338b79ddb87cceae2ae8","tid":450640,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"FF:<br />\n2016年，雲加突然宣佈辭職退休，而對特務工作開始厭倦嘅占士邦係做足半年功課之後，7月1日宣佈接任阿仙奴領隊，誓言要令阿仙奴重新成為爭標分手，並盡最大努力突破歐聯16強<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7fqp9kxa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7fqp9kxa&h=77364a28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一季成績：<br />\n聯賽亞軍，足總盃第5圈出局，聯賽盃亞軍，歐聯16強，mission is yet to complete <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/384swyeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F384swyeg&h=9d896fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攻力不俗，但後防嚴重不穩，聯賽失球數字為前四中最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ekzgxs1l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fekzgxs1l&h=fc411f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k28zoqih\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk28zoqih&h=945c86a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2vsnmual\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2vsnmual&h=17d4ef7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kot5cbe2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkot5cbe2&h=330fb389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aomtfvgh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faomtfvgh&h=20fb0ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sidxp6hj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsidxp6hj&h=037c5c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各進攻球員表現出色 (基奧特除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，韋碧克更成為聯賽神射手同最佳球員，奧斯爾為最佳球員<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tij5o8nf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftij5o8nf&h=3e178221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xtqlbwga\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxtqlbwga&h=8dbfad4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基奧特每次出場都冇貨交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔知是咪單箭頭唔適合佢發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xv458a0s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxv458a0s&h=752f0866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/usd7mzbv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fusd7mzbv&h=051490ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踏入新球季後防依然性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b2fc78ac425517e546368b67b02f2d422f806d","tid":450640,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"Ha"},{"pid":"2d7fc3eac320d37961081ae159c727d9d38744a5","tid":450640,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"Ipad版？"},{"pid":"74843f3f9c96f438e71412bbe7d7d40594d84c0e","tid":450640,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"895f54d99b07c8e3a709d0b4ef8d4cedf6af3953","tid":450640,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ipad版？</blockquote><br />\n我係Android機<br />\n不過D野咪一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977ed9abb9e9633e04e8f4c001099f83a